Alarm0To1Grindottir=GRIMSDOTTIR - Alarm stage 1, Sam, don't be detected!
Alarm0To1Lambert0=LAMBERT - Fisher, you need to be a ghost. You are putting the mission in danger.
Alarm0To1Lambert1=LAMBERT - Fisher, you are paid to be invisible.
Alarm0To1Lambert2=LAMBERT - Be careful Fisher, stealth skills are crucial for this operation.
Alarm0To1BodyFoundLambert=LAMBERT - Fisher, you are taking unnecessary risks when you don't hide the bodies.
Alarm1To2Grindottir=GRIMSDOTTIR - Alarm stage 2. Fisher, if you remain a ghost the alarm stage will decrease.
Alarm1To2Lambert0=LAMBERT - Fisher, the situation will be soon out of control. 
Alarm1To2Lambert1=LAMBERT - Fisher, we cannot afford any more casualties, one more alarm and the mission is over.
Alarm2To3Lambert0=LAMBERT - For Christ sake Fisher, the mission is over.
Alarm2To3Lambert1=LAMBERT - What are you doing, the mission is over.
Alarm1To2BodyFoundLambert=LAMBERT - Fisher, you are taking unnecessary risks when you don't hide the bodies.
Alarm2To3BodyFoundLambert=LAMBERT - Fisher, you need to hide all bodies in the shadows. The mission is over. 
Alarm2To3BodyFoundNote=A body was found, alarm stage increased.
AlarmStageBeforeDecrease=LAMBERT - Fisher, if you can remain undetected, the situation will go back to normal.
AlarmStageAfterDecrease=GRIMSDOTTIR - Okay, it seems they've gone back to normal.
Alarm0To1Enemy=SOLDIER - Security stage increased! Stage 1, flak jacket on!
Alarm1To2Enemy=SOLDIER - Security stage increased! Stage 2, helmet on!
AlarmDecreaseEnemy=SOLDIER - Security stage decreased.
AlarmBackToNormalEnemy=SOLDIER - Security stage back to normal.

